→ Linux/kernel/source/_topics/documentation#linux-kernel-doc[kernel-doc comments], see also → https://github.com/torvalds/linux/blob/master/Documentation/doc-guide/kernel-doc.rst[Documentation/doc-guide/kernel-doc.rst])

